&lt; 2-3-4-5-6 (suit of 2 is tiebreaker; Malaysian variant)<br />\n3-4-5-6-7 &lt; ... &lt; 10-J-Q-K-A &lt; J-Q-K-A-2 (Vietnamese &amp; Indonesian variant)<br />\n3-4-5-6-7 &lt; ... &lt; 10-J-Q-K-A &lt; 2-3-4-5-6 (Suit of 2 is tiebreaker) &lt; A-2-3-4-5 (suit of 2 is tiebreaker; <span style=\"color: red;\">Hong Kong variant</span>)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"Straight (also known as a snake in Cantonese or mokke in Malaysia): Any 5 cards in a sequence (but not all of the same suit). Rank is determined by the value of the biggest card, with the suit used only as a tie-breaker. Therefore 3-4-5-6-7 &lt; 2-3-4-5-6, since 2 is considered the largest card in the 2-3-4-5-6 straight. <span style=\"color: red;\">The largest straight is 2-3-4-5-6, second A-2-3-4-5, third 10-J-Q-K-A while the smallest straight is 3-4-5-6-7.<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n嘈啦，繼續嘈，等睇你條傻狗第時出去撞版畀人屌，又番黎係度呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"笑撚左出聲 我未玩過唔係12345最大既鋤Dee<br />\n或者我未遇到你呢d大陸仔玩開34567大過12345<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe90b8f4268474c0d834413abf2e25e2eb77b0e6","tid":669581,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5ec061ca8d87959c743529e5e5ca33f8d579cddb","tid":669581,"uid":27616,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"係香港我好肯定大部份人玩開都係a2345係最大<br />\n咪撚拎d少數嚟講，我細個捉象棋鍾意玩飛象過河，唔通又可以叫啱？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"小心d 第時同人玩撞版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番大陸果陣"},{"pid":"51150c082fb1ed2c7756a094ac1a51407d161321","tid":669581,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:19:22.000Z","msg":"挫大dee<br />\n<br />\n最大係dee<br />\n<br />\n煙第二大<br />\n<br />\nk&gt;q&gt;j....<br />\n<br />\n同一數字睇花<br />\n<br />\n同一條花